cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.SY, cs.SE 

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics): The paper proposes the use of an autonomous mobile robot equipped with a soil moisture sensor for mapping soil moisture. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The robot is guided by an autonomous exploration strategy driven by the quality of the soil moisture model. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition): Although not the main focus of the paper, the robot may use computer vision techniques for navigation and obstacle avoidance. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper discusses the integration of the sensor measurements into the kriging framework, which is a statistical method used in control systems. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering): The paper may involve software engineering aspects related to the development and implementation of the autonomous exploration strategy and the integration of the sensor measurements into the kriging framework.
